// can try to alter `auth.identities`, `auth.schema_migrations`, etc.
// The Supabase template table `public.profiles` (FK → `auth.users`) forces `auth`
// into `schemas` and blocks public-only push; migration
// `20260509150000_drop_supabase_template_public_profiles` removes it if you still
// use that template. For `auth` in `schemas` without DDL on GoTrue, use Prisma
// 6.13+ externally managed tables (`prisma.config.ts`).
